hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.title: Something Completely Different
hidden_gems_uniform_exploration.description: We picked these out just for you.

289827.title: Mad Money
289827.description: Noticing a flaw in security, three women employed by the Federal Reserve band together to smuggle out millions in bills slated for destruction.

299583.title: The Darkest Hour
299583.description: In this tense apocalyptic thriller, five youths fight to survive after being stranded in Moscow during an alien attack.

300454.title: Moonstruck
300454.description: Loretta Castorini (Cher), a bookkeeper from Brooklyn, New York, finds herself in a difficult situation when she falls for the brother of the man she has agreed to marry.

300459.title: Not Without My Daughter
300459.description: In this thriller based on a true story, an Iranian-American man takes his American wife and daughter to visit Iran, only to keep them hostage there.

300842.title: P2
300842.description: After leaving her office christmas party, a woman must survive the night when she is trapped in a parking garage with a deranged security guard.

304805.title: I'm Gonna Git You Sucka
304805.description: This ultra-hip parody in the tradition of "The Naked Gun" and "Airplane" stars Keenan Ivory Wayans in an action-adventure filled with screwball gags and side-splitting one-liners.

307480.title: The Gallant Hours
307480.description: Based on true events, an American commander in the South Pacific during World War II makes a critical move that helps them defeat the Japanese forces.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

312189.title: Original Gangstas
312189.description: The original members of a notorious gang emerge to take back their town after the current members murder a local boy in this gritty action film.

312423.title: Out of Time
312423.description: Implicated in a suspicious fire, a small-town police chief must stay a step ahead of his own police force to solve a murder and prove his innocence.

334155.title: Igor
334155.description: A mad scientist’s hunchbacked lab assistant enters the Evil Science Fair, dreaming of becoming a mad scientist himself. Can he create a monster?

348926.title: Abandoned
348926.description: When a woman drops off her new boyfriend at the hospital for minor outpatient surgery, she returns to find that he has inexplicably dissappeared.

358575.title: Mississippi Burning
358575.description: Based on the true story, two FBI agents investigate the disappearance of three Mississippi civil rights activists in 1964.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

372440.title: A Turtle's Tale: Sammy's Adventures
372440.description: Sammy the sea turtle and his friend, Ray, swim around the world enduring the challenges of the oceans in search of Shelly, the love of Sammy's life.

389496.title: What's the Worst That Could Happen?
389496.description: A professional thief tries to rob a billionaire's mansion. But when the crook’s lucky ring is stolen, he vows revenge in this laugh-out-loud comedy.

465245.title: Target for Rage
465245.description: A troubled youth, who has been expelled from high school, returns to campus to exact revenge on the teachers he blames for ruining his life.

472710.title: Lionheart
472710.description: After the murder of his brother, a tough soldier goes AWOL and enters the underground world of bare-knuckle fighting to support his family.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

475190.title: Apartment 407
475190.description: Based on true events, a single mother goes to a photo studio for a modeling shoot but gets drugged and sold into sex slavery as she fights to escape.

480226.title: Gacy
480226.description: He appeared to be a model citizen, father, and husband. This film dives into the psyche of this serial killer, who murdered over thirty men and boys.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

495156.title: The Killing Secret
495156.description: When a high school student is suspected of killing a pregnant teen, his girlfriend bonds with the victim’s mother and pieces together the evidence.

495759.title: Shameful Secrets
495759.description: A suburban mother and her kids hide the secret, violent abuse of her husband and escape his wrath only to have to face him in a nasty custody battle.

504505.title: Before the Dawn
504505.description: Lila is a lonely high school teacher who just wants a fresh start, and finds it with Jason, her troubled student who falls for her.

507844.title: After Dark
507844.description: Based on true events, a spring break trip turns tragic when a flat tire and a sinister drifter come before a night that the friends may not survive

515857.title: Scattered Dreams
515857.description: Tenant farmers working hard to provide for their kids are imprisoned by a Florida sheriff for a crime they did not commit and must fight for justice.

520255.title: Dark Skies
520255.description: An average family’s quiet suburban existence begins to unravel when a series of unexplained and terrifying events leave them to fend for themselves.

521035.title: Mac & Devin Go to High School
521035.description: In their senior year, two high school kids, an overachiever working on his valedictory speech, and a stoner who may never graduate, find new paths.

521163.title: Identity Theft
521163.description: The true story of Michelle Brown, who accrues over $50,000 of debt after her identity is stolen, traces her journey and how she helps change laws.

534015.title: The Choice
534015.description: A carefree bachelor and a medical student in her own committed relationship must make a choice of the heart in this heart-lifting romance drama.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

544023.title: The Brothers
544023.description: Engaging romantic comedy about 4 young Black men whose success in life is incomplete, a fact they face when their resident playboy gets engaged.

550792.title: Monster Family
550792.description: At a Halloween costume party, Emma Wishbone and her family fall under the curse of an evil witch who transforms them into real-life monsters.

550826.title: The Hunger Games: Catching Fire
550826.description: As Katniss and Peeta embark on their victory tour, President Snow plans an even deadlier new Hunger Games, which threatens the future of Panem.

554542.title: School Dance
554542.description: Being a high school freshman is no walk in the park, but it’s even tougher as a teenager finds his dream girl and she has no idea he even exists.

555641.title: RV
555641.description: In the spirit of bonding with his dysfunctional family, patriarch Bob rents a motorhome for what becomes a madcap road trip to the Colorado Rockies.

557221.title: Cop Out
557221.description: Bruce Willis and Tracy Morgan star as an oddball pair of NYPD partners who must take on a ruthless, memorabilia-obsessed criminal.

561890.title: Plug Love
561890.description: After a woman ends her unfaithful relationship, she discovers the value of true love in a world that often prioritizes material wealth.

562766.title: The Hammer
562766.description: When a prison boxer turns down freedom, for fighting in the 1984 Olympics, to protect those he loves, he forces his best friend to learn the true meaning of loyalty.

564235.title: A Woman Scorned: The Betty Broderick Story
564235.description: Left by her renowned lawyer husband for his secretary, a scorned San Diego socialite and soccer mom gets the ultimate revenge. Based on a true story.

569452.title: Kevin Hart: Laugh at My Pain
569452.description: The hilarious comic keeps it real by showing his Philadelphia roots, where he first started honing the skills that would make him a comedy superstar.

581905.title: Little Nicky
581905.description: After Satan refuses to retire his post in Hell, he sends the nicest and youngest of his sons to New York City to bring his two renegade brothers home.

586565.title: The Toy
586565.description: A spoiled son of a wealthy man begs his father to buy the friendship and constant companionship of a struggling writer, played by Richard Pryor.

587267.title: The Capture of the Green River Killer
587267.description: Based on the true story of a sadistic serial killer hiding in plain sight in the Northwest U.S., a teen runaway finds her fate headed toward his path.

589474.title: Blood Country
589474.description: In post-Civil War Mississippi, a sheriff is tasked with the manhunt of an escaped convict charged with killing his own brother. Based on a true story.

590086.title: Lie Exposed
590086.description: A woman struggling with alcoholism leaves her husband for a drinking spree in Los Angeles and forms a new relationship with a revealing photographer.

590148.title: Sex and the Future
590148.description: After two men decide to engineer their ideal woman as a robot, a wealthy prince buy is - hoping that they can change the world with artificial sex.

591361.title: Legend of the Tsunami Warrior (Dubbed)
591361.description: An action-packed tale of a brewing, epic war between a port city ruled by a Princess and a brutal pirate brigade led by a Prince and a sorcerer.

594197.title: Deuce Bigalow: European Gigolo
594197.description: Rob Schneider is back as a most unlikely gigolo whose trip to Amsterdam becomes lusty work as he tries to find the killer framing his best friend T.J.

596518.title: Dead Woman's Hollow
596518.description: Based on a true crime, this is the story of two women who are targeted during their Pennsylvania camping trip by a vicious mountain man.

599629.title: Eyes Wide Shut
599629.description: Tom Cruise and Nicole Kidman star as a married couple entangled in an intricate web of jealousy and sexual obsession in Stanley Kubrick's final cinematic offering.  At a Christmas party hosted by wealthy, unconventional Victor Ziegler (Sydney Pollack), provocative advances and innocent flirtations arouse suspicion as high-society physician Dr. William Harford (Cruise) and his sexy wife, Alice (Kidman) watch each other from a distance. Alone later, this seemingly perfect couple confront their intimate sexual fantasies--which don't include each other.  Caught between reality and illusion, jealousy and obsession, William struggles with his inner urges. Will he act on his erotic fantasies or keep them hidden deep inside? Sometimes a man can see more clearly with his Eyes Wide Shut.

599997.title: Wedding Crashers
599997.description: Owen Wilson (Starsky & Hutch) and Vince Vaughn (Old School) star as John Beckwith and Jeremy Klein, two partying divorce attorneys--and committed womanizers--who have figured out a surefire way to meet women: they crash weddings. But the guys' happy-go-lucky lives change abruptly when John unexpectedly falls in love with a bridesmaid (Rachel McAdams - The Notebook). Things become even more complicated when the men discover that the object of John's affection is the daughter of the United States Secretary of the Treasury (Christopher Walken - Catch Me If You Can) in the engaging romantic comedy Wedding Crashers.

604274.title: Erased
604274.description: Ex-CIA operative Ben Logan (Aaron Eckhart, The Dark Knight) has been long estranged from his young daughter (Liana Liberato).

605418.title: 90 Minutes in Heaven
605418.description: Based on the New York Times bestseller, this is the story of a man who comes back to life after a terrible car crash, trusting in God to survive.

605420.title: Street Fighter
605420.description: Jean-Claude Van Damme leads this box-office smash, adapted from the videogame, about a commando and his street fighters out to stop an evil general.

610572.title: Goodfellas
610572.description: Based on a true story, a young man rises up the ranks of a mob family over several years, dabbling in drugs, heists and murders along the way.

611638.title: Son of Bigfoot
611638.description: A teen longs to know his father and sets out on the adventure of a lifetime to find out who he is- only to learn that his old man is Bigfoot!

611824.title: Luis and the Aliens
611824.description: A boy at risk of being sent to boarding school due to his neglectful Dad - and three aliens stranded due to watching too much TV - must help each other out.

614976.title: If You're Gone
614976.description: When a high school senior vanishes on the night of graduation, his girlfriend is forced to question everything she thought she knew about them both.

622272.title: Lockdown: 2025
622272.description: When a highly contagious virus puts the entire country on lockdown, enforced by martial law, one family learns they’re not safe in their own home.

622846.title: Australia
622846.description: With the threat of war looming, a landowner in Australia fights to keep her cattle and her land with the help of a seasoned ranch hand.

628023.title: The Best Little Whorehouse in Texas
628023.description: This rousing musical portrays a sheriff and a madam, who band together to save the infamous Texas Chicken Ranch from a big-city TV crusader.

629889.title: Charley Varrick
629889.description: Walter Matthau plays a petty thief who knocks off a mob bank and soon finds that both the police and a hit man are chasing after him.

631513.title: The People Under the Stairs
631513.description: Wes Craven lures you into the scariest house on the block in a chilling tale of a boy trapped in a home full of nightmarish inhabitants and creatures.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

631924.title: Sebastien (Director's Cut)
631924.description: A woman and her family leave NYC to find a quieter life, but soon become the victims of evil spirits residing in their new home. Based on true events.

639856.title: The Lies He Told
639856.description: The true story of a charming military man, who arranges his own disappearance and fakes his death, to begin a new life with an unsuspecting woman.

639974.title: To Wong Foo, Thanks for Everything! Julie Newmar
639974.description: John Leguizamo, Wesley Snipes, and Patrick Swayze are triple threats in this road trip romp about three drag queens who get stranded in a small town.

641421.title: Tonta Tonta, Pero No Tanto
641421.description: La India Maria decide irse a vivir con una prima a la capital de México para encontrar un buen trabajo, pero surgen toda clase de complicaciones.

645268.title: The Hit List
645268.description: It’s a high-octane race against death when a man meets a hit man in a bar who makes him an offer to kill any five people he wants out of his life.

646042.title: Sparkle
646042.description: Whitney Houston’s final passion project is the remake about a girl group of sisters whose lives are changed forever by the human cost of fame.

646880.title: 616 Wilford Lane
646880.description: Reeling from tragedy, a father and his two teenage daughters start over in rural California in what turns out to be the most haunted house in town.

647078.title: Tales From the Hood
647078.description: Three young thugs show up to an inner-city funeral parlor for a drug pickup and are treated to four tales of horror from its maniacal mortician.

651461.title: A Mother's Rage
651461.description: Lori Laughlin stars as a mother driving her daughter to her new college who ferociously fights off a psychotic person terrorizing them on the highway.

652270.title: The Goonies
652270.description: A pair of brothers hope to save their house by following a treasure map and taking their friends along on a subterranean sea adventure.

654016.title: Something New
654016.description: A workaholic accountant living in Los Angeles must decide between a predictable IBM (Ideal Black Man) and her free-spirited white landscaper.

655009.title: Role Models
655009.description: A destruction of property offense lands a pair of energy drink sales reps a community service sentence as unlikely mentors in a Big Brother program.

655363.title: We Bought a Zoo
655363.description: A single dad set out to give his family a fresh start by uprooting them to the Southern California country to a home in the middle of a neglected zoo.

657674.title: The Edge
657674.description: A plane crash in the Alaskan wilderness pits two enemies and a billionaire against a blood-thirsty Kodiak bear in a brutal struggle for survival.

659846.title: Waiting...
659846.description: A group of young employees at a chain restaurant ponder their lives while dealing with annoying patrons and staving off boredom with antics.

661144.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn: Part 1
661144.description: The fourth film in the Twilight franchise. A marriage, honeymoon and child bring unforeseen and shocking developments for Bella and Edward.

662666.title: The Bye Bye Man
662666.description: Three college friends stumble upon the horrific origins of the Bye Bye Man and learn the only way to avoid his curse: Don't think it; don't say it.

664749.title: 10 Things I Hate About You
664749.description: On the first day at his new school, Cameron instantly falls for Bianca, the gorgeous girl of his dreams. The only problem? She isn't allowed to date.

670370.title: Brightburn
670370.description: What if a child from another world crash-landed on Earth, but instead of becoming a hero to mankind, he proved to be something far more sinister?

675043.title: The Indian in the Cupboard
675043.description: Magic enters the life of a Brooklyn boy on his ninth birthday upon receiving an old wooden cupboard, a set of antique keys and a toy Indian figurine.

675608.title: Saban's Power Rangers
675608.description: Five ordinary teenagers must team together to become something extraordinary in order to save the world from being obliterated by an alien threat.

676858.title: 16 Wishes
676858.description: On her 16th birthday, Abby Jensen's every wish comes magically, wondrously true until one wish too many go wrong and alters everything.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

680256.title: Kevin Hart: Let Me Explain
680256.description: A documentary following Kevin Hart's 2012 international standup comedy tour, which included performances in 80 cities around the globe.

682797.title: Casper
682797.description: Seeing is believing in this adventure about a kind spirit in need of a friend and his ghostly uncles who want all “fleshies” out of their manor.

684103.title: The Lost Tribe
684103.description: Shipwrecked on a remote island, a group of friends discover they are being hunted by a tribe of monstrous, flesh-eating evolutionary throwbacks.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

685151.title: Get Paid
685151.description: A street love story about a broken woman who copes with life by getting paid and falls in love only to find out things aren’t always what they seem.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

694233.title: American Pie Presents: The Book of Love
694233.description: With the help of the legendary Book of Love, three friends embark on an outrageous quest to lose their virginity with the girls of their dreams.

695341.title: Tyler Perry's Why Did I Get Married Too?
695341.description: Four couples on an annual retreat struggle to save their marriages while each of them battles their own financial, physical and emotional issues.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

701100.title: Absence of Innocence
701100.description: Rejected by the woman he wants leads a man who's accustomed to getting his way down the path of increasingly destructive and deadly obsession.

712225.title: Jeepers Creepers 2
712225.description: When their bus breaks down on a deserted road, a team of high school athletes discovers an opponent they cannot defeat and may not survive.

713616.title: Bruised
713616.description: When Kayla discovers that her perfect husband isn't who she thought he was, she’s left with one unthinkable option to end her nightmare.

713924.title: The Preacher's Son
713924.description: Pillars of their community, the Wilson family faces a crisis when their son wrestles with temptation and resists taking over his father’s church.

714235.title: Deadly Secrets
714235.description: When lovers become enemies, friends become foes. A night of fun for a philandering man proves to be a deadly secret in this scandalous drama.

717289.title: Romance
717289.description: A schoolteacher’s frustration with the lack of intimacy in her relationship leads her to seek out excitement through a series of sexual adventures.

720947.title: Little Man
720947.description: After a stolen diamond gets stashed in the home of a husband and wife, a pint-sized jewel thief poses as the world's ugliest baby to get it back.

720949.title: Meeting Evil
720949.description: A man meets a stranger in need of his help, but he finds himself trying to protect his family when the guy turns out to represent unspeakable evil.

720953.title: St. Elmo's Fire
720953.description: Fresh out of college, a sax player, a party girl, a writer, and their other aimless friends search for their places in the real world.

726441.title: Feral
726441.description: A vacation becomes a fight for survival when an animal attacks six medical students on a hike and turns them into rabid, bloodthirsty creatures.

100000260.title: Sebastian
100000260.description: Sebastian, a vengeful spirit that is reborn every 60 years, goes on a pursuit to win the love of Irene, eliminating anyone who gets in his way.

100000286.title: All Things Fall Apart
100000286.description: During his senior year of college, football star Deon is faced with news that could potentially end his future career with an NFL team.

100000360.title: Young & Beautiful
100000360.description: A secretive French teenager chooses sex work over a normal, middle-class life, leading to regular encounters with numerous older men.

100000406.title: Star Slammer
100000406.description: Two women fight off lesbian guards, crazed wardens, and mutant rodents as they struggle to rally their fellow inmates and escape a prison planet.

100000585.title: Gone Before Her Time: Brittany Murphy
100000585.description: Scene-stealing starlet Brittany Murphy was destined for Hollywood’s A-list until her untimely and mysterious death turned out the lights on her lifelong dreams.

100000586.title: Fright Night
100000586.description: Sixteen-year-old Charley Brewster tries to convince everyone that his next-door neighbor is a vampire responsible for a series of unexplained murders.

100000798.title: The Secret She Kept
100000798.description: A successful attorney starts behaving erratically during a political campaign, leading her new husband to suspect she's been hiding a mental illness.

100001038.title: The Heavenly Kid
100001038.description: A lonely teen gets divine intervention when a hip guardian angel trying to earn his wings comes down to teach the high schooler how to be cool.

100001040.title: Chedda Boys
100001040.description: After graduating high school, a basketball prospect eager to make his name decides to help his cousins expand the family drug-dealing business.

100001195.title: Our House
100001195.description: A machine that can bring back dead loved ones seems like a great idea for a young inventor, until he unleashes the wrong spirits in his family home.

100001275.title: Burnt Offerings
100001275.description: When a family rents an isolated country mansion for the summer, they find themselves surrounded by an evil presence that feeds on human suffering.

100001280.title: Go Tell the Spartans
100001280.description: Major Barker reluctantly leads a detachment of troops to an abandoned French outpost in Vietnam, triggering a bloody confrontation with the Viet Cong.

100001288.title: Meteor
100001288.description: An American scientist learns that a huge meteor is hurtling towards Earth, and the only way to stop it is to share nuclear secrets with the USSR.

100001293.title: The People That Time Forgot
100001293.description: In this epic adventure, an expedition searching for a lost explorer stumbles upon a strange oasis in the Arctic inhabited by dinosaurs and cavemen.

100001354.title: Eli Roth Presents: The Stranger
100001354.description: A strange wanderer arrives in town in search of a woman and learns that she is dead. His blood harbors a deadly secret that could rip the town apart.

100001373.title: Kingdom of the Spiders
100001373.description: Two animal experts learn that thousands of tarantulas have changed their eating habits, putting their town at the center of an eight-legged nightmare.

100001394.title: Carnifex
100001394.description: On their quest into the Australian Outback to track the animals left displaced by bushfires, a trio discovers a terrifying species and realize they're the ones being tracked.

100001407.title: Flipped
100001407.description: “Somewhere between confusion and absolute terror,” 8th grader Bryce Loski begins to fall hard for the pesky girl who’s pined for him since age seven.

100001417.title: The Food of the Gods
100001417.description: During a hunting trip on a remote Canadian island, a group of friends must contend with giant, bloodthirsty animals in this cult classic.

100001647.title: Let's Eat
100001647.description: When a struggling real estate agent starts selling guns to make ends meet, his newfound success makes waves in the streets of Richmond, Virginia.

100001695.title: Kisses and Bullets
100001695.description: An Internet model and her roommates invite men to their house to drug and rob them, but their choices lead them to dire consequences.

100001830.title: The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy
100001830.description: Seconds before Earth is destroyed to make way for a new hyperspace express route, a mild-mannered man is whisked off to an intergalactic odyssey.

100001936.title: The Siege
100001936.description: An FBI agent and a CIA operative team up to track down a terrorist cell responsible for a series of attacks in NYC, which is put under martial law.

100001992.title: Illegal Tender
100001992.description: When his family's shadowy past comes back to haunt them, a college student learns the dark source of their wealth and fights off their enemies.

100001993.title: Hanna
100001993.description: Raised in isolation by her father to be the perfect assassin, 16-year-old Hanna sets out on a mission to kill a merciless CIA operative.

100002033.title: You Never Know
100002033.description: Immersed in a world filled with crime, drugs, and betrayal, a group of friends find themselves in too deep when they’re interrogated by a detective.

100002087.title: King Kong
100002087.description: A devious producer leads his crew to an ominous island full of deadly creatures, where a giant ape becomes captivated by the film’s leading lady.

100002097.title: Locked In
100002097.description: When a naive college grad takes a road trip to find herself, she meets a mysterious who girl seduces her down a path of temptation. It’s all fun & games until people start dying.

100002122.title: The North Star
100002122.description: The true story of two slaves, Big Ben Jones and Moses Hopkins, as they escape from a Virginia plantation in 1849 and set off on a journey to freedom.

100002159.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
100002159.description: The Bride continues her quest for revenge, fighting her way through a host of assassins in pursuit of a final showdown with the man who betrayed her.

100002268.title: Those Who Wish Me Dead
100002268.description: A smokejumper working in the Montana wilderness finds a bloodied young boy whom she must protect from two relentless killers and a dangerous wildfire.

100002269.title: The Lego Movie 2: The Second Part
100002269.description: The heroes of Bricksburg reunite to fend off an alien invasion, sending them to a galaxy filled with strange characters and catchy new songs.

100002277.title: The Disappearing Act
100002277.description: Based on a true story, a young man falls for a woman with a dark side. His mother embarks on a tireless search when she stops hearing from him.

100002304.title: Invincible
100002304.description: A 30-year-old bartender and lifelong football fan gets a shot at glory when the Philadelphia Eagles announce that they’re holding open tryouts.

100002338.title: Joe Kidd
100002338.description: A gunslinger is hired by a wealthy land baron to stop the rebellion of local Mexican revolutionaries who claim they’ve been cheated out of their land.

100002532.title: Entre Las Piernas
100002532.description: Dos adictos al sexo comienzan una aventura apasionante. Una de sus vidas se complica cuando algo inesperado aparece en el maletero de un coche.

100002539.title: Make It Out
100002539.description: Star basketball players Treyvon, Xavier, and DJ are the best in the game. But basketball isn't the only game they're playing.

100002565.title: Sticky: A (Self) Love Story
100002565.description: In this stimulating documentary, sexologists, authors, and others explore everything your mother was too embarrassed to tell you about masturbation.

100002566.title: Watch Your Back
100002566.description: As one of Detroit's top strippers, Kanisha effortlessly seduces and manipulates men out of their money to fund her extravagant lifestyle.

100002668.title: Repeater
100002668.description: After a botched job in Colombia, a hitman takes on a high-stakes contract that may have deadly consequences for all involved—himself included.

100002689.title: The Green Knight
100002689.description: King Arthur's headstrong nephew embarks on an epic, daring quest to confront the Green Knight, a mysterious giant who appears at Camelot.

100002884.title: Ghost Rider: Spirit of Vengeance
100002884.description: Struggling to repress the Ghost Rider's curse, Johnny Blaze gets a chance at redemption when a secret sect recruits him to protect a boy from Satan.

100002979.title: Book of Creatures
100002979.description: The Belt, Shiver, Cost of Living and The Demonoids are four stories filled with creatures, critters and other creepy things sure to chill your bones.

100003057.title: A French Maid in San Francisco
100003057.description: A beautiful young French woman travels to San Francisco to find adventure and romance while employed as a maid at several eccentric households.

100003156.title: Back to the Future
100003156.description: Marty McFly is blasted to 1955 in a time machine created by Doc Brown and finds himself in a time-shattering situation that jeopardizes his future.

100003162.title: Pigs
100003162.description: A ladies' man takes a bet to "complete" the alphabet before college graduation. All goes well until he falls for Gabrielle Xeropolos, aka The X.

100003231.title: Bathhouse
